msgid "Network analysis"
msgstr "Analiza mreže"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/networkanalysis.rst:14
msgid "Service area (from layer)"
msgstr "Oblast dostupnosti (iz sloja)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/networkanalysis.rst:15
msgid ""
"Returns all the edges or parts of edges of a network that can be reached "
"within a distance or a time, starting from a point layer. This allows "
"evaluation of accessibility within a network, e.g., what are the places I "
"can navigate to on a road network without spending cost greater than a given"
" value (the cost can be distance or time)."
msgstr ""
"Vraća sve ivice ili delove ivica mreže do kojih se može stići unutar zadatog"
" rastojanja ili vremena, polazeći od tačkastog sloja. Ovo omogućava procenu "
"dostupnosti unutar mreže, npr. do kojih mesta mogu da stignem na putnoj "
"mreži bez utroška većeg od zadate vrednosti (utrošak može biti rastojanje "
"ili vreme)."

