"The values used in this field are specified with the three parameters "
"``Value for forward direction``, ``Value for backward direction`` and "
"``Value for both directions``. Forward and reverse directions correspond to "
"a one-way edge, \"both directions\" indicates a two-way edge. If a feature "
"does not have a value in this field, or no field is set then the default "
"direction setting (provided with the ``Default direction`` parameter) is "
"used."
