#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/networkanalysis.rst:270
msgid ""
"Returns all the edges or parts of edges of a network that can be reached "
"within a given distance or time, starting from a point feature. This allows "
"the evaluation of accessibility within a network, e.g., what are the places "
"I can navigate to on a road network without spending a cost greater than a "
"given value (the cost can be distance or time)."
msgstr ""
"Vraća sve ivice ili delove ivica mreže do kojih se može stići unutar zadatog"
" rastojanja ili vremena, polazeći od tačkastog objekta. Ovo omogućava "
"procenu dostupnosti unutar mreže, npr. do kojih mesta mogu da stignem na "
"putnoj mreži bez utroška većeg od zadate vrednosti (utrošak može biti "
"rastojanje ili vreme)."

